          <div class = "text"> <h1 style = "font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 30px;">Emilia Romagna Grand Prix Race  </h1>
             
              <P>The race started at 16:30 local time on 23 April and lasted for 21 laps.</p>
               <P>The race was won by Max Verstappen, ahead of Sergio Pérez and Lando Norris in second and third, respectively. </p>
                 <P>Max Verstappen had a bad start and Charles Leclerc took the lead but Verstappen overtook Leclerc on lap 19
                 </P>
                 
                 <P> This therefore lead to Verstappen winning</P> 
                 <P>This served as Red Bull Racing's first 1–2 finish since the 2016 Malaysian Grand Prix,as well as Verstappen's second career grand slam</P>
                 <P> Max Verstappen had the fastest lap at time:   1:18.446 on lap 55.</P>
